snippet.title: RC Stunt Copter (ACE MODE) - Playstation 1
snippet.description: There are numerous people on YouTube vids claiming this Playstation game is "impossible" or "unplayable", which is totally untrue and I prove it with this video. I really like this game and it's mostly fun to play with awesome commentry of American humour, although challenging at times. Watch me playing in ACE mode and completing each level pretty much with ease, all it takes is a bit of practice andf patience. I got to level 5 and decided the video was getting too long so didn't do a complete walkthrough which may have taken a lot longer.
